WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:22.000
I have some more of the white particles in view below the capsule. They appear to be traveling exactly my speed. There is one drifting off. It's going faster than I am, as a matter of fact.

00:22.000 --> 00:40.000
Roger. Understand. I haven't seen the great numbers of these particles, but I have seen a few of them. Their motion is random. They look exactly like snowflakes to me.

00:40.000 --> 00:50.000
Roger. Have you tried returning? Negative. Let me get within scanner limits first.

00:50.000 --> 01:00.000
Say yes. I must adjust my attitude to within scanner limits first.

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
Roger.

01:20.000 --> 01:38.000
There were some more of those little particles. They definitely look like snowflakes this time.

01:38.000 --> 01:46.000
Roger. I understand your particles look like definite snowflakes. However...

01:46.000 --> 01:48.000
Mr. Scott? Roger.

01:48.000 --> 01:56.000
Mr. Scott?

01:56.000 --> 01:58.000
Mr. Scott?

01:58.000 --> 02:00.000
Mr. Scott?

